<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Provide a retail platform to other services vendors</title>
    <para>
        REMIG is considering to levarage its infrastructure around billing, collection, metering and reporting in order to provide
        other vendors with less developed infrastructures a retail platform from which they could sell their services. This may include,
        for example, billing and collection around rates and taxes, water, rentals and other services.
    </para>
</section>    
